Morphological characteristics of sea cucumbers (Holothuroidea) from Socah Waters, Bangkalan, Madura

Sea cucumbers belong to the Phylum Echinodermata with unique and diverse body shape. At the organism level, phenotype is an attribute or characteristic that can be seen, observed, or measured.
